---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Team | Cloud Identity Summit 2026">
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 px-4 overflow-hidden flex-grow text-center">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-3xl h-[400px] bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-900/30 via-cyan-900/10 to-transparent blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="inline-block bg-cyan-900/30 border border-cyan-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-6">
                <span class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">The Organizers</span>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight mb-8">
                By the Community.<br/>
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500">For the Community.</span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                The Cloud Identity Summit was born out of a shared passion for cloud security, Entra ID, and architecture. Meet the team working behind the scenes to bring this conference to life.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-32 w-full relative z-10">
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
                
                <div class="mb-6 relative z-10">
                    <img src="/images/team/gregor.jpg" alt="Gregor Reimling" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-slate-700 group-hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors mx-auto shadow-lg" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' viewBox=\'0 0 100 100\'><rect width=\'100\' height=\'100\' fill=\'%231e293b\'/><text x=\'50\' y=\'50\' font-family=\'Arial\' font-size=\'40\' fill=\'%23475569\' dominant-baseline=\'middle\' text-anchor=\'middle\'>GR</text></svg>'"/>
                </div>
                
                <div class="text-center mb-6 relative z-10 flex-grow">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Gregor Reimling</h3>
                    <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Microsoft MVP | Chief Azure Technologist</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Gregor is a Microsoft MVP in Azure and Security, and Chief Azure Technologist at adesso SE. He leads technical strategy and implementation for Azure, focusing on enterprise-scale architectures, cloud security, and governance. As a Microsoft Certified Trainer (MCT), he empowers professionals through hands-on training and mentorship worldwide.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 relative z-10 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50">
                    <a href="https://sessionize.com/GregorReimling" target="_blank" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors" title="Sessionize Profile">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm-1-7c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1s.45-1 1-1 1 .45 1 1-.45 1-1 1zm5 7h-2v-6h2v6zm-1-7c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1s.45-1 1-1 1 .45 1 1-.45 1-1 1z"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
                
                <div class="mb-6 relative z-10">
                    <img src="/images/team/thomas.jpg" alt="Thomas Naunheim" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-slate-700 group-hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors mx-auto shadow-lg" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' viewBox=\'0 0 100 100\'><rect width=\'100\' height=\'100\' fill=\'%231e293b\'/><text x=\'50\' y=\'50\' font-family=\'Arial\' font-size=\'40\' fill=\'%23475569\' dominant-baseline=\'middle\' text-anchor=\'middle\'>TN</text></svg>'"/>
                </div>
                
                <div class="text-center mb-6 relative z-10 flex-grow">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Thomas Naunheim</h3>
                    <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Microsoft MVP | Cyber Security Architect</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Thomas is a Cyber Security Architect at glueckkanja AG and a Microsoft MVP specializing in cloud-native identity and security solutions in Entra ID and Azure. He is a passionate community contributor, blogger at cloud-architekt.net, co-host of the "Cloud Inspires" podcast, and co-author of the Entra ID Attack & Defense Playbook.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 relative z-10 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50">
                    <a href="https://sessionize.com/ThomasNaunheim/" target="_blank" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors" title="Sessionize Profile">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm-1-7c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1s.45-1 1-1 1 .45 1 1-.45 1-1 1zm5 7h-2v-6h2v6zm-1-7c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1s.45-1 1-1 1 .45 1 1-.45 1-1 1z"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
                
                <div class="mb-6 relative z-10">
                    <img src="/images/team/rene.jpg" alt="René Wasel" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-slate-700 group-hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors mx-auto shadow-lg" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' viewBox=\'0 0 100 100\'><rect width=\'100\' height=\'100\' fill=\'%231e293b\'/><text x=\'50\' y=\'50\' font-family=\'Arial\' font-size=\'40\' fill=\'%23475569\' dominant-baseline=\'middle\' text-anchor=\'middle\'>RW</text></svg>'"/>
                </div>
                
                <div class="text-center mb-6 relative z-10 flex-grow">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">René Wasel</h3>
                    <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Microsoft MVP | M365 Specialist</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Working in IT since 2002, René is a Microsoft 365 Specialist and awarded MVP. He has a deep technical focus on the modern workplace cosmos. Beyond his technical expertise, René is a true community driver: He co-hosts the podcast "Daniel und René - M365 im Alltag" and passionately organizes multiple local tech meetups and user groups.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 relative z-10 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/50">
                    <a href="https://sessionize.com/ReneWasel" target="_blank" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors" title="Sessionize Profile">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm-1-7c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1s.45-1 1-1 1 .45 1 1-.45 1-1 1zm5 7h-2v-6h2v6zm-1-7c-.55 0-1-.45-1-1s.45-1 1-1 1 .45 1 1-.45 1-1 1z"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </main>
</Layout>